Tutorial:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jAE94gzgQvI&list=PL4cUxeGkcC9ib4HsrXEYpQnTOTZE1x0uc&index=2

Installation:
pip install django

Create basic Django Project:
django-admin startproject basicProjDjango

Then navigate to the project and execute the command:
python manage.py runserver

Create another folder:
python manage.py startapp articles

Whenever we add any model we need to add migrations:
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate

